FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our food app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the food app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our food app allows you to browse restaurants, view menus, place orders, and track deliveries all in one place. Simply download the app, create an account, and start exploring delicious options in your area.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Is there a minimum order amount?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Minimum order amounts may vary depending on the restaurant. You can check the minimum order requirement for each restaurant on their menu page within the app.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How can I track my order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Once your order is confirmed, you can track its status in real-time through the app. You'll receive notifications for order acceptance, preparation, and when your food is out for delivery.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: We accept various payment methods including credit/debit cards, digital wallets, and cash on delivery (where available). You can manage your payment options in the app settings.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How can I contact customer support?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: For any issues or queries, you can reach our customer support team through the 'Help' section in the app. We also offer 24/7 chat support and a dedicated customer service hotline for immediate assistance.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our food app connects you with local restaurants and eateries, allowing you to browse menus, place orders, and have delicious meals delivered right to your doorstep. Simply download the app, create an account, and start exploring culinary options in your area.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Is there a minimum order amount?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Minimum order amounts may vary depending on the restaurant and your location. You can easily check any minimum order requirements before finalizing your purchase within the app.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How long does delivery usually take?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Delivery times can vary based on factors such as distance, traffic, and restaurant preparation times. On average, most orders are delivered within 30-45 minutes. You can track your order in real-time through the app to get an accurate estimate.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I customize my order or make special requests?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! Many restaurants on our platform offer customization options for their dishes. You can add special instructions or requests in the notes section when placing your order. Keep in mind that some modifications may incur additional charges.
